OL,6,FITV Channel reporter Matthew Leach
OL,7,Fwrites:
OL,9,FParishes are calling for more
OL,10,Frepresentation in central government
OL,11,Fas Guernsey heads to its second island-
OL,12,Fwide election in June.
OL,14,FIt comes as St Martin's Douzaine
OL,15,Fstarted work on a community plan after
OL,16,Fa disagreement on where affordable
OL,17,Fhousing should be built.
