OL,3,CGuernsey parishes call for more
OL,4,Crepresentation in central government
OL,6,FGuernsey Douzaines are responsible for
OL,7,Fplenty, but do they have enough power
OL,8,Fand representation in central
OL,9,Fgovernment?
OL,11,FSt Martin Constable Samantha Bauer
OL,12,Fsaid: "This came about because last
OL,13,Fsummer, the IDP review was to build a
OL,14,Flot of affordable housing on the
OL,15,Fperiphery of the parish.
OL,17,F"It was something they didn't know
OL,18,Fabout in advance and it generated a
OL,19,Flot of concern."
