OL,3,CGuernsey parishes call for more
OL,4,Crepresentation in central government
OL,6,FVoters would therefore cast their
OL,7,Fballots for people close to them
OL,8,Fgeographically so that Deputies could
OL,9,Frepresent them on important parochial
OL,10,Fissues.
OL,12,FA referendum in 2018 cut this
OL,13,Fconnection by introducing island-wide
OL,14,Fvoting.
OL,16,FNow, people can vote for anyone,
OL,17,Fanywhere and it has had several
OL,18,Funintended consequences.
