OL,3,CGuernsey parishes call for more
OL,4,Crepresentation in central government
OL,6,FThe shift to island-wide voting saw a
OL,7,Fcollapse in the number of Deputies
OL,8,Fvoted in from the northern parishes.
OL,10,FIn 2016 the northern parishes of St
OL,11,FSampson and Vale had 12 Deputies -
OL,12,Fthis fell by half to only six
OL,13,Ffollowing the election in 2020.
OL,15,FIn contrast, the southern and western
OL,16,Fparishes increased from 10 Deputies in
OL,17,F2016 to 17 in 2020.
OL,19,FDeputies are invited to parish
OL,20,Fmeetings but the setup is not perfect.
